123
00:05:28,022 --> 00:05:31,414
desperately finding a way to save his country

124
00:05:32,943 --> 00:05:33,860
The restoration of Zhang Xun

125
00:05:33,861 --> 00:05:35,072
signaled that

126
00:05:35,073 --> 00:05:37,457
the plan for the establishment of a bourgeois republic in China

127
00:05:37,471 --> 00:05:38,715
