130
00:05:42,486 --> 00:05:44,786
and caused a change in perception and criticism

131
00:05:45,143 --> 00:05:46,365
The modern Chinese

132
00:05:46,366 --> 00:05:47,612
started to realize 

133
00:05:47,613 --> 00:05:49,046
that just relying on transplanting

134
00:05:49,047 --> 00:05:50,875
